title: Available 6/1/2016 - Flowmaster Outlaw Cat-back - 2005-2010 Mustang GT w/ 4.6L or 5.4L V8 - 817515
description:
Flowmaster Outlaw Cat-back exhaust system for the 2005-2010 Mustang GT with 4.6L or 5.4L V8, part# 817515


Flowmaster Part #817515

Application:
Fits 2005-2010 Ford Mustang GT with a 4.6L or 5.4L V8 engine

Special Note:
This system also fits convertible and GT500 models

Description:
Flowmaster’s new Outlaw Cat-back exhaust system for the 05-10 Ford Mustang GT is perfect for the person looking for a very deep and aggressive sound level outside and inside the car with all of the performance benefits that you would expect from Flowmaster.

This exhaust is not for the faint of heart! This bolt-on DOR (Dual Out Rear) emissions-legal system for cars with the 4.6L or 5.4L V8 engine features a pair of race proven Outlaw Series mufflers and dual mandrel bent 2.50” tailpipes for maximum performance. The system is built out of 409S stainless steel and utilizes 4.00” polished stainless steel Flowmaster embossed tips. This exhaust system also fits convertible and GT500 models. 

The exhaust system is manufactured in the USA and is covered by Flowmaster’s Lifetime lImited Warranty. Designed for an easy fit, this system includes all necessary parts and hardware for installation. 

-Stainless Steel Construction
-Dyno Tuned for Maximum Performance
-True Bolt-on Installation
-Made in the USA

Please call 707-544-4761 or visit www.flowmastermufflers.com for additional application and product information.
